        "text": "In your Campaign Log, record <i>Eliyah has confronted his demons</i>. Draw a checkmark next to his name in the Expedition Team section.\nFrom now on, whenever Eliyah Ashevak is included or used during a scenario, use the set-aside [[Resolute]] version instead of the version from the <i>Expedition Team</i> encounter set. If he is currently in play, switch him with that version now.\nAdd this card to the victory display.\nThe investigators may advance the current act or continue playing.",
        "realText": "In your Campaign Log, record <i>Eliyah has confronted his demons</i>. Draw a checkmark next to his name in the Expedition Team section.\nFrom now on, whenever Eliyah Ashevak is included or used during a scenario, use the set-aside [[Resolute]] version instead of the version from the <i>Expedition Team</i> encounter set. If he is currently in play, switch him with that version now.\nAdd this card to the victory display.\nThe investigators may advance the current act or continue playing.",
