        "name": "The Supplicant's Evidence",
        "realName": "The Supplicant's Evidence",
        "text": "<hr><b>After an investigator has \"sabotaged the train,\" read the following (if this task has already been completed, read the following immediately):</b>\n<blockquote><i>You manage to corner Dr. Moore as he tries to escape the city on foot. \"Very clever,\" he admits. \"But you're already out of time. Lock me up, it doesn't matter. The dreamers will be sacrificed, and our Chosen will lead us to a new age.\" But after several hours, he is begging to be let out of the city. \"Please, the reaper is coming! Neith is coming for us all. We'll all be sacrificed, don't you understand? You and me both! All of us need to flee the city while we still can!\"</i></blockquote>\nRemove 1 strength from the abyss. (Group limit once per game.)",
        "realText": "<hr><b>After an investigator has \"sabotaged the train,\" read the following (if this task has already been completed, read the following immediately):</b>\n<blockquote><i>You manage to corner Dr. Moore as he tries to escape the city on foot. \"Very clever,\" he admits. \"But you're already out of time. Lock me up, it doesn't matter. The dreamers will be sacrificed, and our Chosen will lead us to a new age.\" But after several hours, he is begging to be let out of the city. \"Please, the reaper is coming! Neith is coming for us all. We'll all be sacrificed, don't you understand? You and me both! All of us need to flee the city while we still can!\"</i></blockquote>\nRemove 1 strength from the abyss. (Group limit once per game.)",
